SELECT game_id, date, home_team, away_team, home_score, away_score, (SELECT MIN(date) FROM games) AS earliest_date
FROM games
WHERE date = (SELECT MIN(date) FROM games);

external_knowledge:
The top players here refer to those who rank in the top three based on average passing yards within their respective teams;
The number of games played refers to the total games a player has participated in;
Average passing yards per player is the total passing yards divided by the number of games played.

